{
  "stem": "11882.5",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they loved America.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We went down there, the first time on a 4th of July.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And we were-- America was just fated, you know.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Some of the staff in the big trial were Czechoslovaks, also, that had been in exile during the war in America-- or sometimes in England.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And we'd go to Garmisch-Partenkirchen.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Let's see, to Berchtesgaden.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Once in a while to-- this was different times during that period-- to Switzerland.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Weekends were a big thing, to be able to go away, you know.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "We began to get cars.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "They were distributed.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "We had to pay for them, of course.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "The army distributed them in a lottery.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "You would draw numbers, you know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And once I won a car-- I bought a Pontiac.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "In those days, a Pontiac cost $1,700 at the most.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Things were different in those days, you know?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then you could drive all over Europe.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And aside from the terrible condition of the roads, there was no traffic problem whatsoever.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There were a few German cars on the road, but very little.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But the condition of the roads was appalling-- as the condition of the telephones was.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "One day in winter, before the big trial ended, I called up Ingemaus.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Ingemaus had stayed through the war in Germany, and the Germans would not allow her to marry her semi-- partly Jewish friend-- fiance.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But she managed, I think, with her resoluteness, and her toughness to keep him going.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He survived the war.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And Ingemaus got married just in time for the baby to arrive, by an American military pastor.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "What do you call it?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Clergyman, you know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "What we would call a chaplain.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And drove in a difficult-- took a difficult drive from Hamburg to Bremen.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
